Mini User Management System ‚Äì Frontend

This is the frontend application of the Mini User Management System, built using React (Vite).
It provides user interfaces for authentication, navigation, and protected pages, and communicates with a Node.js + MongoDB backend.

üöÄ Tech Stack------------------------------------------------------

React 18

Vite

React Router DOM v6

Axios

Context API

CSS (Custom Styling)

Features--------------------------------------------------------------------

User Login and Signup UI

JWT-based authentication flow

Protected routes (Dashboard & Profile)

Global authentication state using React Context API

Navigation bar with conditional rendering

Logout functionality

Clean and responsive UI

üîê Authentication Flow-------------------------------------------------------

User registers or logs in

Backend returns a JWT token

Token is stored in authentication context

Protected routes are accessible only for authenticated users  
